data.description: Come one come all to this incredible property situated in the Leinkauf Historic District. This beautiful historic home features large open rooms, beautiful hardwood floors, and a kitchen waiting for your personal touch. Updated features include pool pump and resurface paint, new roof and exterior painting, as well as interior painting. HVAC and electrical have also been updated. Downstairs bathroom has been updated with an added walk in shower. This home has ample possibilities and can be restored to its glory in no time. Buyer to verify all measurements.  Call your favorite agent and schedule your showing today!
